Today morning while travelling back to Thailand I found I didn't took my portable charger after reaching the airport. Then I visited the digital gadgets at terminal 4 to purchase a new power bank, their staff Mr basil shown their different types and explained well about all. Then I purchased their own brand one with MAGSAFE charging. Later I use it and found good capacity and fast charging. I strongly recommend this product to everyone because it's fast charging with 20k capacity and lite weight also
Staff was friendly and helpfull, products were also great! Thankyou Godwin..
